                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="element">
                    <h3>
                        Tailor-Made
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        We ask enough questions before starting a project to know all about your needs and requirements.
                        This makes sure that the content aligns with your brand's goals.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="element">
                    <h3>
                        Fully Managed
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        You don't need to manage writers and their gigs as we provide fully managed content writing
                        services. Focus on the things that you are good at and let us do the content part for you.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>


        <div id="contact">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <div class="mainbody">
                <div class="left">
                    <h1 class="leftin">Let's talk about everything!</h1>
                    <p class="leftin para">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Repudiandae, ad.</p>
                    <img class="leftin image"
                        src="https://preview.colorlib.com/theme/bootstrap/contact-form-16/images/undraw-contact.svg"
                        alt="">
                </div>

                <div class="right">
                    <form class="form" action="/send">

                        <input class="input" type="text" name="name" required placeholder="Name" />

                        <input class="input" type="text" name="email" required placeholder="E-mail" />
